## Testing Pagination

```ruby
test "navigates through pages" do
  visit articles_url
  
  assert_selector ".article", count: 10
  
  click_link "Next"
  
  assert_current_path articles_path(page: 2)
  assert_selector ".article", count: 10
end
```

